EXTERNAL SERVICES

This tool makes runtime requests to external services for diagnostic
purposes. No user credentials are transmitted. The user's public IP
address may be visible to these services as part of standard HTTPS
requests.

4. Cloudflare Speed Test
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Used for bandwidth estimation via HTTPS download.
https://speed.cloudflare.com/
Subject to Cloudflare Terms of Service: https://www.cloudflare.com/terms/

5. GeoIP Providers (cascading fallback)
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Used to determine the user's public IP and approximate geographic
location for network path analysis. The user's public IP address is
sent to these services.

- ipinfo.io (primary) — https://ipinfo.io — Terms: https://ipinfo.io/terms
- freeipapi.com — https://freeipapi.com
- geojs.io — https://get.geojs.io — Terms: https://www.geojs.io/docs/v1/endpoints/geo/
- ipwho.is — https://ipwho.is — Terms: https://ipwho.is/
- ipapi.co — https://ipapi.co — Terms: https://ipapi.co/terms/

6. Google DNS-over-HTTPS
------------------------------------------------------------------------
Used for CNAME chain resolution to identify Traffic Manager routing.
https://dns.google/
Subject to Google Terms of Service: https://policies.google.com/terms

